      "role": "user",
      "content": "the hotline thing just feels like a script. it doesn't change the fact that the person who made my entire life make sense is just... gone. i wake up and for a split second i forget, and then the reality hits and it's like being crushed all over again. i'm just so tired of the crushing. it's like there's no point in even trying to get through the next hour, let alone the next year.",
